      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.1984570343
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ芽衣、準備してくるね！\n紅茶に合うおすすめのドーナツ持って来るよー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "じゃあ芽衣、準備してくるね！\n紅茶に合うおすすめのドーナツ持って来るよー",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.3462345281
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "ソファでごろーんって寝っ転がってのんびり待ってて\n今、みんな出掛けてるし、気にしなくて大丈夫だからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ソファでごろーんって寝っ転がってのんびり待ってて\n今、みんな出掛けてるし、気にしなくて大丈夫だからね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6387.098805200005,
          "startTime": 49.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.7452364761
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "本格的にくつろぐ訳には……ってもう行ったのか\n余程、ドーナツを一緒に食べたかったんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "本格的にくつろぐ訳には……ってもう行ったのか\n余程、ドーナツを一緒に食べたかったんだな",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_night",
      "startTime": 62.6365087032
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "じゃーん！\nおかわり出来るようにいーっぱい持って来たよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "じゃーん！\nおかわり出来るようにいーっぱい持って来たよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.8666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "おお、早いなって……お、おい！？\nどうしたんだ、それ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "おお、早いなって……お、おい！？\nどうしたんだ、それ！？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.4333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "目の付け所が違うねー！　最近近所に出来た\nドーナツ屋さんの名物・オールドファッションだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "目の付け所が違うねー！　最近近所に出来た\nドーナツ屋さんの名物・オールドファッションだよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.6333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "そのまま食べても美味しいんだけど、紅茶に浸す\nダンシングって食べ方がおススメなんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そのまま食べても美味しいんだけど、紅茶に浸す\nダンシングって食べ方がおススメなんだって",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.8666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "えーっと、多分ダンキングのことか？\n確か紅茶やミルクに浸す食べ方……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "えーっと、多分ダンキングのことか？\n確か紅茶やミルクに浸す食べ方……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.5666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いや、そうじゃなくて俺が言ってるのは格好の方だ！\nどうして突然着替えて来たんだ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "いや、そうじゃなくて俺が言ってるのは格好の方だ！\nどうして突然着替えて来たんだ！？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.0333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、どうかな？　{user}さんを\nおもてなしするために着てみたんだー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "えへへ、どうかな？　{user}さんを\nおもてなしするために着てみたんだー",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.3333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
